            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13292543">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">美和审美在对象和主题方面的共同特点为积淀：内容积淀为形式，想象、观念积淀为感受。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-06-12 10:45</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>美和审美在对象和主题方面的共同特点为积淀：内容积淀为形式，想象、观念积淀为感受。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
